## SPLITS

  `Ctrl+Shift+Enter`      New split
  `Ctrl+Shift+W`          Close split
  `Ctrl+Shift+]`          Focus next split
  `Ctrl+Shift+[`          Focus previous split
  `Ctrl+Shift+R`          Resize mode
  `Ctrl+Shift+F7`         Visually move split
  `Ctrl+Shift+Alt+T`      Set split title

## TABS

  `Ctrl+Shift+T`          New tab
  `Ctrl+Shift+Q`          Close tab
  `Ctrl+Shift+Right`      Next tab
  `Ctrl+Shift+Left`       Previous tab
  `Ctrl+Shift+Alt+T`      Rename tab
  `Ctrl+Shift+1-9`        Jump to tab by number

## MISC

  `Ctrl+Shift+C`          Copy
  `Ctrl+Shift+V`          Paste
  `Ctrl+Shift+=`          Increase font size
  `Ctrl+Shift+-`          Decrease font size
  `Ctrl+Shift+Backspace`  Reset font size
  `Ctrl+Shift+F11`        Toggle fullscreen
  `Ctrl+Shift+U`          Unicode input
